title: When is urf coming out
body: Im wondering when is URF coming out and why there wasn't any game modes live this week?

replies.body: If you refer to the patch notes for 7.24 (specifically the "[Upcoming Events](https://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/patch/patch-724-notes#patch-upcoming-events)" section) you'll notice it tells you that URF (rather, Snow Battle ARURF) will be available from 20/12/17 at 3:00 am AEDT until 3/1/18 at 2:55am AEDT, so it's about a week away. For the rest of the "Snowdown Season" (13/12/17 to 9/1/18), Legend of the Poro King will be available to play.
P R A N K E D
They don't do urf any more.
